The paper discusses a recommendation system that combines latent factor models with semi-supervised learning. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning and specifically relates to recommender systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses information retrieval (IR) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which are relevant sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of graphs, which is a topic in both social networks (cs.SI) and data structures (cs.DS).
